'''Black demons''' are one of the strongest demons that inhabit multiple dungeons throughout [[RuneScape Classic]]. They are quite dangerous and caution should be taken if you are fighting them. A level 175 black demon is fought during the [[The Grand Tree (quest)|Grand Tree]] quest.

==Locations==
*[[Edgeville dungeon]] (level 156, [[Wilderness]])
*[[Grand Tree dungeon]] (level 175, only during [[The Grand Tree (quest)|The Grand Tree quest]])
*[[Ogre Enclave]] (caged)
*[[Taverley dungeon]]

